page.title: 08Inside Joanna's House.
page.content: Detached. 10 rooms. KITCHEN........Cooker,Fridge,Dishwasher and Television. BOILER ROOM....Freezer,Boiler and Washing Machine. LOUNGE.........3 Piece Suite,Television Piano,Fireplace,Desk,and Hi-Fi System. HALL...........Chest of Drawers and a Telescope. PARENT'S ROOM..Double Bed,Chest of Drawers,Wardrobe,Mirror and Dressing Table. SARAH'S ROOM...Cabin Bed,Shower,Sink, and Rocking Chair. EMILY'S ROOM...2 Single Beds,Wardrobe, Chest Of Drawers & Desk. JOANNA'S ROOM..Single Bed,Wardrobe & Hi-Fi. BATHROOM.......Bath,Bidet & Shower. DINING ROOM....Table and Chairs.
